"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Negotiations are happening in Islamabad, but not much is known about them. Sources say that three parties are involved in the talks.\",            \"english_title\": \"Talks in Islamabad\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hay negociaciones en Islamabad, pero no se sabe mucho sobre ellas. Fuentes dicen que tres grupos est\u00e1n en las conversaciones.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Conversaciones en Islamabad\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Four astronauts returned to Earth after a nine-day trip. They traveled further from Earth than any humans before.\",            \"english_title\": \"Astronauts Return\",            \"translated_version\": \"Cuatro astronautas regresaron a la Tierra despu\u00e9s de un viaje de nueve d\u00edas. Viajaron m\u00e1s lejos de la Tierra que cualquier humano antes.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Regreso de Astronautas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A woman has become involved in the Epstein case, opposing the administration that wants to stop the investigation.\",            \"english_title\": \"Woman in Epstein Case\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una mujer est\u00e1 involucrada en el caso Epstein, oponi\u00e9ndose a la administraci\u00f3n que quiere parar la investigaci\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Mujer en Caso Epstein\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Judges have given sentences from five years to life in prison after large trials.\",            \"english_title\": \"Judges Give Sentences\",            \"translated_version\": \"Jueces han dado sentencias de cinco a\u00f1os a cadena perpetua despu\u00e9s de grandes juicios.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Jueces Dan Sentencias\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A Haitian migrant, who was previously protected from being sent back, is accused of killing a woman at a gas station in Florida.\",            \"english_title\": \"Migrant Accused\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un migrante haitiano, que antes estaba protegido de ser enviado de regreso, es acusado de matar a una mujer en una gasolinera en Florida.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Migrante Acusado\"        }    ]}"